OL,6,FSpeaking about the outcome, Chief
OL,7,FOfficer Damian Kitchen said: "Guernsey
OL,8,FPolice quite rightly expects the
OL,9,Fhighest standards of professional
OL,10,Fbehaviour from its officers and staff,
OL,11,Fas do the communities we serve and
OL,12,Fprotect.
OL,14,F"The force cannot and will not
OL,15,Ftolerate behaviour of this kind. We
OL,16,Fwill always take action to protect our
OL,17,Fofficers, staff, and without question,
OL,18,Fthe public.
